00:28:06.720 --> 00:28:11.309
Second of all,
we took the intuitively simple

00:28:11.309 --> 00:28:14.960
plot of scale factor versus
time,

00:28:14.960 --> 00:28:17.172
which actually tells you what
you need to know about the

00:28:17.172 --> 00:28:19.299
Universe: is it getting bigger?
Is it getting smaller?

00:28:19.299 --> 00:28:20.500
Is it going to have a Big
