so as to flatten out one of the

00:28:43.542 --> 00:28:45.900
lines.
Okay?

00:28:45.900 --> 00:28:49.250
So, it's a three-part exercise
in confusion.

00:28:49.250 --> 00:28:54.992
And I would say that the number
one conceptually difficult thing

00:28:54.992 --> 00:29:00.370
in this entire course is to
